  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "A+TRohh5/q5jeCFew7DtKSFhTlqJ3ff+crHUaSlv43c=",
    "originContent": "#### Troubleshooting",
    "translatedContent": "#### 故障排除"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "choxCqVK7MpfMJFJNKRfHxBJMD8qyACzE9LRisq5EL0=",
    "originContent": "- **All of the icons are hazard (⚠️) symbols.**",
    "translatedContent": "- **所有图标都是警告（⚠️）符号。**"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "drTKxAMPHJffPqlzXgNR7Zlgdnx68nd/9/3gRG25PqU=",
    "originContent": "    - As of version v1.0.5, the icons should be installed automatically, however if you are still encountering this issue, try manually copying the icons from the `zzz-readermenuredesign.koplugin` folder and putting them into the KOReader icons folder `/koreader/resources/icons`.",
    "translatedContent": "    - 从 v1.0.5 版本开始，图标应自动安装，但如果仍遇到此问题，请尝试手动将图标从 `zzz-readermenuredesign.koplugin` 文件夹复制到 KOReader 图标文件夹 `/koreader/resources/icons`。"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "zGxZJfV5gIq5VZRQdjLR8EK09uBSnPVyxFxQHlM8ZfM=",
    "originContent": "- **Icons are not showing at all**.",
    "translatedContent": "- **图标根本不显示。**"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "05XXPgdMez/Kk/iTV4Rlh3WZS8I9f/Cc9uFFaEZyFlA=",
    "originContent": "    - This can happen on some devices with older versions of this plugin. Try deleting this plugins SVG icons from `/koreader/resources/icons/mdlight` and replace them with the PNG icons from the [latest release](https://github.com/kristianpennacchia/zzz-readermenuredesign.koplugin/releases/latest), then **restart KOReader**.",
    "translatedContent": "    - 这可能发生在某些设备使用旧版本插件时。尝试删除 `/koreader/resources/icons/mdlight` 中此插件的 SVG 图标，并用[最新版本](https://github.com/kristianpennacchia/zzz-readermenuredesign.koplugin/releases/latest)中的 PNG 图标替换，然后**重启 KOReader**。"
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
